OL,3,CRussia 'may strike British bases' and
OL,4,Cplans tactical nuclear weapon drills
OL,6,Fhas threatened to strike British
OL,7,Fmilitary bases and said it would hold
OL,8,Fdrills simulating the use of
OL,9,Fbattlefield nuclear weapons amid
OL,10,Fsharply rising tensions over comments
OL,11,Fby senior Western officials about
OL,12,Fpossibly deeper involvement in the war
OL,13,Fin Ukraine.
