OL,3,CRussia 'may strike British bases' and
OL,4,Cplans tactical nuclear weapon drills
OL,6,FAfter summoning the British ambassador
OL,7,Fto the Foreign Ministry, Moscow warned
OL,8,Fthat Ukrainian strikes on Russian
OL,9,Fterritory with UK-supplied weapons
OL,10,Fcould bring retaliatory strikes on
OL,11,FBritish military facilities and
OL,12,Fequipment on Ukrainian soil or
OL,13,Felsewhere.
OL,15,FThe drills are a response to
OL,16,F"provocative statements and threats of
OL,17,Fcertain Western officials regarding
OL,18,Fthe Russian Federation," the Defence
OL,19,FMinistry said in a statement.
