OL,3,CRussia 'may strike British bases' and
OL,4,Cplans tactical nuclear weapon drills
OL,6,FForeign Secretary David Cameron
OL,7,Frecently said Kyiv's forces will be
OL,8,Fable to use British long-range weapons
OL,9,Fto strike targets inside Russia.
OL,11,FIt was the first time Russia has
OL,12,Fpublicly announced drills involving
OL,13,Ftactical nuclear weapons, although its
OL,14,Fstrategic nuclear forces regularly
OL,15,Fhold exercises.
OL,17,FTactical nuclear weapons include air
OL,18,Fbombs, warheads for short-range
OL,19,Fmissiles and artillery munitions and
OL,20,Fare meant for use on a battlefield.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/6
