OL,3,CRussia 'may strike British bases' and
OL,4,Cplans tactical nuclear weapon drills
OL,6,FThey are less powerful than the
OL,7,Fstrategic weapons - massive warheads
OL,8,Fthat arm intercontinental ballistic
OL,9,Fmissiles and are intended to
OL,10,Fobliterate entire cities.
OL,12,FThe Russian announcement was a warning
OL,13,Fto Ukraine's Western allies about
OL,14,Fbecoming more deeply engaged in the 2-
OL,15,Fyear-old war, where the Kremlin's
OL,16,Fforces have gained an upper hand amid
OL,17,FUkraine's shortage of manpower and
OL,18,Fweapons.
