OL,3,CRussia 'may strike British bases' and
OL,4,Cplans tactical nuclear weapon drills
OL,6,FSome of Ukraine's Western partners
OL,7,Fhave previously expressed concern that
OL,8,Fthe conflict could spill beyond
OL,9,FUkraine into a war between NATO and
OL,10,FRussia.
OL,12,FKremlin spokesman Dmitry Peskov said
OL,13,Fon Monday that statements by British
OL,14,Fofficials and a comment by French
OL,15,FPresident Emmanuel Macron about
OL,16,Fpossibly sending soldiers to help in
OL,17,FUkraine had prompted the drills.
