OL,6,F"It's a new round of escalation,"
OL,7,FPeskov said, referring to what the
OL,8,FKremlin regarded as provocative
OL,9,Fstatements. "It's unprecedented and
OL,10,Frequires special attention and special
OL,11,Fmeasures."
